Package org.freeinternals.format.classfile.constant

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CONSTANT_Class_info
    The class for the CONSTANT_Class_info structure in constant pool.
    CONSTANT_Double_info
    The class for the CONSTANT_Double_info structure in constant pool.
    CONSTANT_Dynamic
    Parent of The CONSTANT_Dynamic_info and CONSTANT_InvokeDynamic_info structures.
    CONSTANT_Dynamic_info
    The CONSTANT_Dynamic_info structure is used to represent a dynamically-computed constant, an arbitrary value that is produced by invocation of a bootstrap method in the course of an ldc instruction, among others.
    CONSTANT_Fieldref_info
    The class for the CONSTANT_Fieldref_info structure in constant pool.
    CONSTANT_Float_info
    The class for the CONSTANT_Float_info structure in constant pool.

    CONSTANT_InterfaceMethodref_info
    The class for the CONSTANT_InterfaceMethodref_info structure in constant pool.
    CONSTANT_InvokeDynamic_info
    The CONSTANT_InvokeDynamic_info structure is used by an invokedynamic instruction to specify a bootstrap method, the dynamic invocation name, the argument and return types of the call, and optionally, a sequence of additional constants called static arguments to the bootstrap method.

    The class for the CONSTANT_Long_info structure in constant pool.
